Watch as our moonshiners stumble into a series of mishaps. Donnie and Teresa deliver moonshine to an old friend but come up a gallon short and must see if he’ll accept it anyway. Josh and Colt scramble to fill a 60-gallon order for the Moonshine Bandits while another moonshiner accidentally burns his arm as even more trouble unfolds.
